    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you ready to fall in love with your next ride? I\u2019m listing my absolute pride and joy, and honestly, she\u2019s a total dream. This car has been pampered since day one and looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor\u2014not a single scratch or speck of dust in sight! It drives like a cloud and feels absolutely brand new. I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, and I\u2019m looking for someone who will appreciate it just as much as I have. Come take a look, you won\u2019t be disappointed!",
      "price": 44900.0,
