      "description": "Hey there! You\u2019ve gotta see this beauty in person. I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, and it\u2019s still in total mint condition\u2014honestly, it feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It\u2019s super clean, runs like a dream, and is totally ready for its next adventure. I\u2019m looking for a smooth sale to someone who will love it as much as I have, so come grab this gem while it\u2019s still here!",
